# Force HTTPS
http://* https://:splat 301!

# Redirect pages.dev to Custom Domain
# Explicit subpath redirects first to ensure they are caught
https://blogolog.pages.dev/blog/* https://blogolog.com.tr/blog/:splat 301!
https://blogolog.pages.dev/tags/* https://blogolog.com.tr/tags/:splat 301!
# Global catch-all
https://blogolog.pages.dev/* https://blogolog.com.tr/:splat 301!

# WWW to Non-WWW
https://www.blogolog.com.tr/* https://blogolog.com.tr/:splat 301!

# Remove Trailing Slash (exclude static assets)
# This rule matches explicit trailing slashes on non-asset paths
/*/ /:splat 301! 

# Custom Redirects
/blog/kahve-nasil-demlenir https://blogolog.com.tr/blog/kahve-nasil-yapilir 301
/blog/kahve-nasil-demlenir/ https://blogolog.com.tr/blog/kahve-nasil-yapilir 301

# Temporary Redirects
/about / 302
/about/ / 302
